intent.user_query: what are the top 5 products based on revenue generated?

phases.goal: Retrieve the top 5 products based on revenue generated from the SaleDetails and Products tables in the fitness_db database.

arguments.sql: SELECT p.ProductID, p.ProductName, SUM(sd.Quantity * sd.UnitPrice) AS TotalRevenue FROM fitness_db.Products p JOIN fitness_db.SaleDetails sd ON p.ProductID = sd.ProductID GROUP BY p.ProductID, p.ProductName ORDER BY TotalRevenue DESC LIMIT 5;

phases.goal: Generate the final report based on the data gathered.
